            <title>[SPR-11767] Move Spring Boot&apos;s YAML properties into the core framework.</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-11767</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When depending spring-context, I want to be able to pull configuration out of YAML files like I could be able to with *.properties files.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
